{"tid":2451945,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"昂山素姬將被加控貪腐罪名","createTime":"2021-03-18T12:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T12:46:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"643beb39857a1c408f1bc7e7be4368f08948b5a0","tid":2451945,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T12:46:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581269-20210318.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581269-20210318.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2dXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=04c5745e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581269-20210318.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bead1347\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581269-20210318.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n緬甸民眾反軍事政變的示威持續，外電報道，被軍方扣押的國務資政昂山素姬，將會被加控涉及貪腐罪名。昂山素姬的代表律師批評，控罪是沒有根據和不合邏輯。<br />\n<br />\n軍方上星期指昂山素姬涉嫌受賄60萬美元與一批黃金。當地軍方電視台昨晚播放片段，表示一名緬甸商人承認在過去數年，向昂山素姬共支付55萬美元的捐款。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，軍方連日武力鎮壓示威，至今造成超過200人死亡，但實際死亡數字可能更高。報道表示，當地的互聯網服務進一步受到限制，私營報章的發行亦受到禁制。"}]}